        "## Creating a train and a validation data\n",
        "\n",
        "Recall that we would like to train the model on earlier time periods and test it on later ones. To this end, we make the split using the code below.\n"
      ],
      "id": "1d758529"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
